#* The impact of ambiguity and redundancy on tag recommendation in folksonomies
#@ Jonathan Gemmell;Maryam Ramezani;Thomas Schimoler;Laura Christiansen;Bamshad Mobasher
#t 2009
#c 9
#% 268079
#% 375017
#% 869504
