#* Experimental comparison of pre- vs. post-filtering approaches in context-aware recommender systems
#@ Umberto Panniello;Alexander Tuzhilin;Michele Gorgoglione;Cosimo Palmisano;Anto Pedone
#t 2009
#c 9
#% 522882
#% 801785
