#* Do clicks measure recommendation relevancy?: an empirical user study
#@ Hua Zheng;Dong Wang;Qi Zhang;Hang Li;Tinghao Yang
#t 2010
#c 9
#% 220711
#% 452563
#% 452664
#% 734590
