#* Increasing consumers' understanding of recommender results: a preference-based hybrid algorithm with strong explanatory power
#@ Paul Marx;Thorsten Hennig-Thurau;André Marchand
#t 2010
#c 9
#% 280852
#% 314933
#% 345371
#% 790459
