#* Xbox movies recommendations: variational bayes matrix factorization with embedded feature selection
#@ Noam Koenigstein;Ulrich Paquet
#t 2013
#c 9
#% 303620
#% 414514
#% 770816
#% 840924
#% 891559
#% 1042718
